    <h1>Application</h1>
    
    <h2>Become a part of Global Shapers Copenhagen</h2>

    <p>If you are in your 20s, based in Copenhagen and have the drive to achieve something extraordinary with social impact, then we would love to hear from you. We do not care what field of study/work you are in or if you plan to impact 5 or 50.000 people – we want to hear what makes you tick and how joining our community will enable you to achieve your goals. 
We take in new applicants twice a year. Next intake is in October – the application deadline is October 7th. 
Let us know how the World Economic Forum network can help you create the impact you would like to see by filling out our application form <a href="https://projectaccess.typeform.com/to/d1vbiw?">here</a>.</p>
